> His gameplay is toxic, usually you cannot send one person to deal with them, he constantly goes top and has such an amazingly reliable escape. So when your team fight the enemy 4v5 and they kite you around, tryndamere will be sitting top whacking your towers. Its awful. Is god awful. It makes me more uncomfortable than anything else in this game.

